$ PowerShell: the preference variable $MaximumDriveCount

The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference[preference variable] `$maximumDriveCount` specifies how many
→ Windows/PowerShell/language/provider/drive[drives] are allowed in a → Windows/PowerShell/session[session].

sa:
  → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference[Preference variables]
